# 詞: 睇怕

1. 我睇怕今晚會落大暴雨，大家最好帶返把遮先。 (I'm afraid it's going to rain heavily tonight, so everyone should bring an umbrella.)
2. 佢睇怕呢個項目做唔到，所以想放棄。 (He's afraid that this project won't work out, so he wants to give up.)
3. 睇怕我哋遲咗，個戲已經開場咗。 (I'm afraid we're late; the movie has already started.)
4. 你睇怕唔係佢嘅錯，係個系統出咗問題。 (I'm afraid it's not his fault; the system has a problem.)
5. 睇怕呢間餐廳今晚客滿，我哋要轉去邊度食飯。 (I'm afraid this restaurant is fully booked tonight; we need to find somewhere else to eat.)
6. 佢睇怕自己考唔過呢科試，成日都喺度溫書。 (He's afraid he won't pass this exam, so he's studying all the time.)
7. 睇怕呢個計劃行唔通，我哋要重新諗過。 (I'm afraid this plan won't work; we need to rethink it.)
8. 你睇怕佢唔會答應你嘅要求，因為佢好固執。 (I'm afraid he won't agree to your request because he's very stubborn.)
9. 睇怕呢個天氣好差，我哋唔好出街啦。 (I'm afraid the weather is terrible; let's not go out.)
10. 佢睇怕自己搞唔掂呢個工作，所以請咗人幫手。 (He's afraid he can't handle this job, so he asked for help.) [end of text]


